<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Roth Conversion Strategy — {{ firm_name }}</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bronze: #867550;
    --bronze-dark: #6b5d3f;
    --ink: #232020;
    --charcoal: #32373c;
    --paper: #f5f5f5;
    --rule: #d9d4c7;
    --warning: #8a3a2c;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  html, body {
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', -apple-system, sans-serif;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: #e9e6df;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .page {
    width: 8.5in;
    min-height: 11in;
    margin: 24px auto;
    background: var(--paper);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .masthead {
    background: #000;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 28px 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--bronze);
  }
  .mark { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px; }
  .mark svg { width: 44px; height: 52px; }
  .wordmark {
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .wordmark span {
    display: block; font-weight: 300; font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--bronze); letter-spacing: 0.22em; margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .doc-label {
    text-align: right; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bronze); font-weight: 500;
  }
  .doc-label strong {
    display: block; color: #fff; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em; margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .client-strip {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    padding: 18px 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); background: #fff;
  }
  .client-strip .cell { font-size: 11px; }
  .client-strip .cell .label {
    color: var(--bronze); text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em; font-weight: 600; font-size: 9px; margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .client-strip .cell .value { font-weight: 500; font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink); }

  .recommendation { padding: 36px 48px 28px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .eyebrow {
    color: var(--bronze); text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em; font-weight: 600; font-size: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .headline {
    font-size: 28px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.25;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0; color: var(--ink); max-width: 640px;
  }
  .headline .amount { color: var(--bronze); font-weight: 600; }
  .rationale {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.6; max-width: 620px; font-weight: 300;
  }

  .signature {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.1fr;
    padding: 32px 48px; background: #fff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    gap: 40px; align-items: center;
  }
  .signature .lever-label {
    color: var(--bronze); text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em; font-weight: 600; font-size: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .signature .lever-copy {
    font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--charcoal); font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Chart */
  .chart-wrap { padding-left: 8px; }
  .chart-title {
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--bronze);
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.22em; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .chart-legend {
    display: flex; gap: 18px; font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--charcoal); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 500;
  }
  .chart-legend .swatch {
    display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px;
    margin-right: 6px; vertical-align: middle; border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .chart-legend .swatch.without { background: var(--warning); }
  .chart-legend .swatch.plan { background: var(--bronze); }
  .chart-labels {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 9px; color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-top: 6px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .schedule { padding: 28px 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--bronze);
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.22em; margin: 0 0 14px 0;
  }

  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; }
  thead th {
    text-align: left; font-weight: 600; font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em; color: var(--ink);
    padding: 10px 12px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--bronze); background: #fafaf7;
  }
  thead th:nth-child(n+3) { text-align: right; }
  tbody td { padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); font-weight: 400; }
  tbody td:nth-child(n+3) { text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  tbody tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  tbody td.convert-amount { font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink); }

  .schedule-total {
    margin-top: 12px; padding: 10px 12px; background: var(--ink); color: #fff;
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  }
  .schedule-total .total-value {
    color: var(--bronze); font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0; text-transform: none; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .tradeoff {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    padding: 28px 48px; gap: 40px; background: #fff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .tradeoff .col h3 {
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em; color: var(--bronze); margin: 0 0 10px 0;
  }
  .tradeoff .col p {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; font-weight: 300;
  }
  .tradeoff .col p strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }

  .foot {
    padding: 22px 48px 28px; margin-top: auto;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--bronze); background: #000; color: #fff;
  }
  .foot .advisor-line {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline;
    font-size: 11px; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .foot .advisor-line strong {
    letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 10px;
  }
  .foot .advisor-line span { color: var(--bronze); }
  .disclosure { font-size: 8.5px; color: #9a9388; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 300; }

  @media print {
    body { background: #fff; }
    .page { margin: 0; box-shadow: none; }
    @page { size: letter; margin: 0; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="page">

  <header class="masthead">
    <div class="mark">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
        <rect x="6" y="4" width="88" height="10" fill="#867550"/>
        <path d="M 10 22 L 10 68 Q 10 98 50 114 Q 90 98 90 68 L 90 22 Z"
              fill="none" stroke="#867550" stroke-width="4.5"/>
        <text x="50" y="72" text-anchor="middle"
              font-family="Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif"
              font-size="46" font-weight="400" fill="#867550">R</text>
        <rect x="42" y="80" width="16" height="2.5" fill="#867550"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="wordmark">
        {{ firm_name_line_1 }}<br>{{ firm_name_line_2 }}
        <span>{{ firm_tagline }}</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-label">
      <strong>{{ report_date }}</strong>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="recommendation">
    <div class="eyebrow">Our Recommendation</div>
    <h1 class="headline">
      Convert <span class="amount">{{ total_conversion_usd | currency_exact }}</span> from your Traditional IRA to a Roth IRA over the next {{ conversion_years_count_word }} years.
    </h1>
    <p class="rationale">
      Your Required Minimum Distributions start at age {{ rmd_start_age }}. On a {{ starting_ira_usd | currency_short }} IRA, they grow aggressively each year and push your income into progressively higher tax brackets. This plan reduces what the IRS forces you to withdraw later by moving those dollars now, at much lower rates.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="signature">
    <div class="lever">
      <div class="lever-label">Why This Matters</div>
      <p class="lever-copy">
        Without action, RMDs climb every year &mdash; and so does the bracket you&rsquo;re taxed in.{% if without_plan_at_age_80 %} By age 80, &ldquo;do nothing&rdquo; pushes you into the {{ without_plan_at_age_80 | pct }} bracket.{% endif %}{% if without_plan_at_age_85 %} By age 85, the {{ without_plan_at_age_85 | pct }} bracket.{% endif %} This plan holds you at <strong>{{ plan_top_bracket_pct | pct }} or below</strong> for life by pre-paying tax on terms you choose.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="chart-wrap">
      <div class="chart-title">Your Top Marginal Bracket by Age</div>
      <div class="chart-legend">
        <span><span class="swatch without"></span>Without This Plan</span>
        <span><span class="swatch plan"></span>With This Plan</span>
      </div>
      <svg viewBox="0 0 320 140" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
           style="width:100%; height:auto; display:block;">
        <!-- Y gridlines -->
        <line x1="40" y1="20"  x2="310" y2="20"  stroke="#e3dfd4" stroke-width="1"/>
        <line x1="40" y1="50"  x2="310" y2="50"  stroke="#e3dfd4" stroke-width="1"/>
        <line x1="40" y1="80"  x2="310" y2="80"  stroke="#e3dfd4" stroke-width="1"/>
        <line x1="40" y1="110" x2="310" y2="110" stroke="#e3dfd4" stroke-width="1"/>

        <!-- Y labels -->
        <text x="34" y="23"  text-anchor="end" font-size="9" fill="#32373c" font-family="Poppins">37%</text>
        <text x="34" y="53"  text-anchor="end" font-size="9" fill="#32373c" font-family="Poppins">32%</text>
        <text x="34" y="83"  text-anchor="end" font-size="9" fill="#32373c" font-family="Poppins">24%</text>
        <text x="34" y="113" text-anchor="end" font-size="9" fill="#32373c" font-family="Poppins">22%</text>

        <!-- Without plan (stepped, ascending) -->
        <polyline points="{% for pt in bracket_by_age_points %}{{ pt.x }},{{ pt.y_without }}{% if not loop.last %} {% endif %}{% endfor %}"
                  fill="none" stroke="#8a3a2c" stroke-width="2.5"
                  stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        {% for pt in bracket_by_age_points %}
        <circle cx="{{ pt.x }}"  cy="{{ pt.y_without }}" r="3" fill="#8a3a2c"/>
        {% endfor %}

        <!-- With this plan -->
        <polyline points="{% for pt in bracket_by_age_points %}{{ pt.x }},{{ pt.y_with }}{% if not loop.last %} {% endif %}{% endfor %}"
                  fill="none" stroke="#867550" stroke-width="2.5"
                  stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        {% for pt in bracket_by_age_points %}
        <circle cx="{{ pt.x }}"  cy="{{ pt.y_with }}" r="3" fill="#867550"/>
        {% endfor %}

        <!-- X axis line -->
        <line x1="40" y1="125" x2="310" y2="125" stroke="#232020" stroke-width="1"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="chart-labels">
        {% for pt in bracket_by_age_points %}
        <span>{% if loop.first %}Age {% endif %}{{ pt.age }}</span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="schedule">
    <h2 class="section-title">Your {{ conversion_years_count_word_title }}-Year Conversion Schedule</h2>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th style="width: 12%;">Year</th>
          <th style="width: 12%;">{{ age_column_header }}</th>
          <th style="width: 26%;">Conversion</th>
          <th style="width: 25%;">Top Marginal Bracket</th>
          <th style="width: 25%;">Medicare IRMAA Tier</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for row in schedule_rows %}
        <tr>
          <td>{{ row.year }}</td>
          <td>{{ row.age_display }}</td>
          <td class="convert-amount">{{ row.conversion_usd | currency_exact }}</td>
          <td>{{ row.bracket_pct | pct }}</td>
          <td>{{ row.irmaa_tier_mult | irmaa_tier }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <div class="schedule-total">
      <span>Total Converted by RMD Age</span>
      <span class="total-value">{{ total_conversion_usd | currency_exact }}</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="tradeoff">
    <div class="col">
      <h3>What It Costs</h3>
      <p>
        An additional <strong>{{ first_year_conversion_tax_usd | currency_approx }}</strong> in federal tax this year, and a temporary increase in Medicare premiums of roughly <strong>{{ annual_medicare_irmaa_usd | currency_approx_no_tilde }}/year</strong> for the years a conversion is reported.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <h3>What It Preserves</h3>
      <p>
        A lifetime ceiling at the <strong>{{ plan_top_bracket_pct | pct }} bracket</strong> instead of climbing into {{ without_plan_late_bracket_display }}, meaningfully smaller Required Minimum Distributions from age {{ rmd_start_age }} onward, and a larger Roth balance your heirs inherit tax-free.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="foot">
    <div class="advisor-line">
      <strong>{{ firm_name }}</strong>
      <span>{{ firm_website }}</span>
    </div>
    <p class="disclosure">
      {{ disclosure_text }}{% for note in extra_disclosure_notes %} {{ note }}{% endfor %}
    </p>
  </footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>
